Here is how I listen this song -
Step 1.  Start the song listen till end
Step 2.  rewind to 5:30 (enters Mr. Iyer)
Step 3   Redo Step 2 at least 10 times
Step 4   Go back to step 1
Step 5   Repeat the whole thing again.

Hats of to Darshan and Sanket on percussion.. 
Amit Trivedi, Mili, and Shriram...Similar to all the other songs (Badri, Rabba....) this is timeless :)
